name: Pcahan1.github.io
body: ### pcahan1 code @ gitHub Most of this code hosted here is related to my research in Computational and Systems Biology. You can find out more about this research at my Google Scholar webpage ### CellNet CellNet is a network biology-based computational platform designed to estimate the extent to which endogenous, cell type specific gene regulatory networks have been established in user-provided gene expression profiles.
